Cyberpunk style: A dramatic night scene of a futuristic Southeast Asian cityscape with towering neon-lit skyscrapers reflecting off rain-slicked streets. In the foreground, a massive holographic display projects an intricate web of interconnected nodes and pathways resembling a constitutional flowchart or organizational hierarchy, glowing in electric blue and magenta against the dark urban canyon. Citizens with umbrellas gather below, their silhouettes dwarfed by the overwhelming governmental architecture above. The composition emphasizes the tension between individual figures at street level and the imposing institutional structures looming overhead, with dramatic lighting cutting through atmospheric haze and steam rising from street vents.
